      "comment": "BALMAIN BOY (8) was beaten for speed from wide out but attacked the line strongly to place, 5.5 lengths from the winner (22.45) at this track in Maiden. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can measure up this time. JANE'S MAGIC (7) is looking to continue her winning ways off a quick 21.72 victory in a Maiden at this track. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. COME ON CRITTER (6) had second look this course and distance latest and improved on her time, finishing a 9 length third in 22.36. Expecting another bold showing. GOLDSTAR IMOGEN (2) was out of the money at this circuit when making debut but can do much better this time.",
